READING AND WRITING FILES :

how to join folder name name to make a path : os.path.join

get current working directory : os .getcwd

change directory : os.chdir

make directory : os.makedirs

os.path.basename(): curent file/folder

os.path.dirname(): path to that folder

os.path.splt(): to split into tuple base and dir

get size and list dir in python : os.path.getsize() os.listdir

how to get total  size of any directory --> for loop-->lisdir-->getsize-->os.path.join --> ++counter

